    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n6844" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀπάζω</span></b>  (cf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἕπω</span>), fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀπάσσω</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὤπασα,
            ὄπἁσ̓σα</span>, mid. pres. part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀπαζόμενος</span>, fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀπάσσεαι</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀπάσσατο</span>,
          part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὀπασσάμενος</span>: I. act.,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">join as companion</span> (<span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">guide, escort</span>),
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινά τινι</span> (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἅμα, μετά</span>), <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">cause to follow</span> or
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">accompany</span>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            13.416</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 15.310</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 24.153</span></i>, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">461</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 10.204</span></i>; then of
          things, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">bestow, lend, confer;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κῡδός τινι, χάριν καὶ κῦδος ἔργοις, γ
            57</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 15.320</span></i>, w. inf.,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 23.151</span></i>; also <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">follow hard
            upon, press upon.</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινά</span>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            8.341</span></i>; fig., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">γῆρας</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 4.321</span></i>; pass., <i><span class="en">Il. 11.493</span></i>.—II. mid., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">take with
            one</span> (as companion, guide, escort), <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινά,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Il. 10.238</span></i>, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc"> Τ
            238</span>, <i><span class="en">Od.
          10.59</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
